Re: Beta?

Bitcointalk

2010-06-27 12:43:50 UTC - [11]Original Post

   But 1.0 sounds like the first release.  For some things newness is a
   virtue but for this type of software, maturity and stability are
   important.  I donʼt want to put my money in something thatʼs 1.0.  1.0
   might be more interesting for a moment, but after that weʼre still 1.0
   and everyone who comes along thinks we just started.  This is the third
   major release and 1.3 reflects that development history.  (0.1, 0.2,
   1.3)
